    "category": "職場與學習",
    "summary": "整理 agenda、clarify、follow up 等高頻詞，附上不過度正式的實用例句。",
    "publishedDate": "2026-07-16",
    "updatedDate": "2026-07-16",
    "author": "職場編輯部",
    "heroImage": null,
    "tags": [
      "英文",
      "會議",
      "職場"
    ],
    "contentType": "useful",
    "relatedArticles": [],
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "text": "開場與議程"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "items": [
          "agenda 議程：Let’s go through today’s agenda first.",
          "objective 目標：The main objective of this meeting is to confirm the launch date.",
          "update 進度更新：Could you give us a quick update?"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "text": "討論與確認"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "items": [
          "clarify 釐清：Could you clarify what you mean by “ready”?",
          "concern 顧慮：My main concern is the delivery timeline.",
          "option 選項：We have two practical options.",
          "agree on 達成共識：Can we agree on the next step today?"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "text": "收尾與追蹤"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "items": [
          "action item 待辦事項：Let’s review the action items before we finish.",
          "follow up 後續追蹤：I’ll follow up by email tomorrow.",
          "deadline 截止日：The deadline is Friday afternoon.",
          "minutes 會議紀錄：I’ll share the meeting minutes after the call."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "note",
        "text": "會議英文的重點是清楚，不是把每句話變得很長。先說結論，再補原因與下一步，通常比堆疊艱深單字有效。"
      }
    ]
  },
